From a0b59604bcf24b13af168fa45d54bbedab1d3d5d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Dan Bloomberg <dan.bloomberg@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 27 Jan 2021 15:10:15 -0800
Subject: [PATCH] Fix issue 29819: Heap-buffer-overflow in fdilate_1_56 *
 Illegal use of a function; fix documentation to reflect this. * Fix some bugs
 in flipdetect_fuzzer and pix3_fuzzer. * Limit size of sel generated from a
 template pix. * Remove large output data in dwamorph1_reg, unless display is
 requested * Added new reg test: binmorph6_reg.c

